title: Avison Young's Kevill: Urbanization Causes Rental Growth(Audio)

(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: John Kevill, Head of US Capital Markets for Avison Young, on the commercial real estate outlook, the future for the Washington DC market, and what types of buildings are selling.
